{"type": "article", "id": 47879, "title": "《你的名字》制片为 Tiffany 拍广告，肯德基推出加菲猫玩偶 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-12-04T04:39:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 925, "name": "圣诞节"}, {"id": 1941, "name": "肯德基"}, {"id": 2601, "name": "宝马"}, {"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 48, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171204123233AzdGXMBwlHtYqmfo.gif", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MzYxMjI0NQ==&amp;mid=2659126532&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=61f089421d31d83211233b826a9b2372&amp;chksm=bd1fc5be8a684ca880ae06d097d5cec3fd05be83fb21503835d1dd301e53b88d00bcc61d0449&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1204P4koqCEPiIwTDas0aN6t&amp;key=cb709b928d46332ca000fa071ec85c2414be73a2fb491ce8ce483bd43542e6970552f64a9bdec4efb3c420e9f709321235f8780bcad975c8fe421ac466927a7e95c7ac54504606d20770eeb6f55521cc&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;pass_ticket=3Fs8bZTlFzym%2BAWKkMwu4RFgCpNMwO6BTQ%2Fj2a76qaUuObnERhQZkFAQRG9DeZZs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>肯德基X加菲猫X乐事薯片</b></a>：肯德基圣诞季营销，推出两款加菲猫玩偶，还有一款和乐事大波浪薯片合作的新品热辣薯片脆皮鸡。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017120412324849yoAMUld6IaQiL0.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.442786\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24261.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>《你的名字》制作人川村元气为 Tiffany 拍摄了一支微电影广告</b></a>，男女主角分别由日本人气偶像成田凌、杉咲花出演。这支广告是为了呼应每年 11 月 22 日是日本“好夫妻日（いい夫婦の日）”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=g0512s6t222&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://brandchannel.com/2017/11/30/benetton-oliviero-toscani-reunited-113017/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>曾为贝纳通拍摄无数举世闻名广告海报的摄影师、艺术总监 Oliviero Toscani 最近重新和这家意大利服装品牌展开合作</b></a>。新的广告中，来自 13 个国家，4 个大洲的 28 名意大利小学的学生都穿着贝纳通的衣服，展示包容的精神。不过比起当年极具冲击力的视觉表达，这次 Toscani 的作品温和了许多。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204122150RfShqiNy8C4nZHOW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204122202Uu0n5co6yReGF19O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.696875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24215.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">独立创意机构 F5 为百度拍的广告片</a></b>，讲述一位货车司机风雪夜归的故事，等待他的妻子、女儿和母亲也彻夜未眠，为他担忧祈福。广告主打的是影片中的疲劳驾驶监测系统，主题为 “AI，让每个人安全回家”。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a0513wz0ox5&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24264.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>MINI 做了一个汽车植物图鉴的平面广告</b></a>，把 8 种适合车载的植物和 MINI 汽车结合在一起做了一组海报，还挺别致。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121042HeaUMRgYLzw01CQf.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.620000\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121204lzidSkoyrXvc0aBe.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121216N4VWh9ULX0BEuFkj.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121224fjLbnMegqd1asCwv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121229x49pRWDCFkcB6UQJ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121238vpR59IofBYMr3xXe.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121244xcYQMk6j3HsNegiK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204121307VQANbZ57OjCtDUIm.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712041213178cbHtYuSsa9KJFek.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186250\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 16.0px 'Lantinghei SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 22.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2017/nov/29/coca-cola-christmas-truck-tour-criticised-obesity-tooth-decay\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>有 22 年历史的可口可乐英国圣诞卡车（到处免费派发可乐）最近受到英国国家健康局的抵制</b></a>，认为这种高糖饮料的促销行为对当地的孩子有负面影响；可口可乐随后决定在派发种类里增加 Diet Coke 等低糖选项。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171204122025Ayrz12WqIwehLP6v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.600000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2017/12/03/unilever-taps-mindshare-for-global-communications-planning/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>过去一周，群邑旗下媒介购买公司传立媒体相继拿下欧莱雅在中国、联合利华在全球的代理业务。</b></a>在此之前，欧莱雅中国的绩效营销（Search）和电子商务两块业务由阳狮旗下的 Performics 负责，其他归传立打理，这也是过去 10 年欧莱雅首次将所有媒介业务交给一家公司；而联合利华原先的全球传播策略业务在 PHD 手中。<br></p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/online-ad-prices-rise-as-industry-combats-counterfeit-inventory-google-says-1512068974\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Google 表示，随着程序化广告标准 Ads.txt 的推行</b></a>，过去三周通过 Google 程序化广告购买系统成交的数字广告平均价格有所上升，这被认为是打击广告欺诈有了成效的标志。<br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：MINI</p>"}